data.description: Double the opportunity for the price of one!  Experience the best of both worlds with this charming two-unit brick building complemented by a two-unit coach house. Each unit in the main building boasts a warm ambiance with a living room, formal dining room, three bedrooms, and a bath- each adorned with some elegant hardwood floors.  The frame Coach house in the rear, featuring two units and enclosed porches, adds a touch of uniqueness to the property, offering a floor plan designed for creativity and versatility. Beyond the property, enjoy the convenience of proximity to a park, school, public transportation, and local businesses-all within a short, pleasant walking distance. Don't miss out-schedule your tour now and seize this exceptional opportunity!
